Package com.pranab.playwithgraphs.datastructure.implementation

Class DoubleEndedNode<V>

java.lang.Object
com.pranab.playwithgraphs.datastructure.implementation.DoubleEndedNode<V>
Type Parameters:
V - - The object that needs to be saved in collection
public class DoubleEndedNode<V>
extends java.lang.Object
The object of this class is basic building unit for DynamicList data structure. This object is a double end node storing a reference to previous and next node. Also encapsulates the value
Author:
Pranab Bharadwaj
